— | 32–36 | Gem
17–24 | 37–41 | Jester
25–32 | 42–46 | Key
33–40 | 47–51 | Knight
41–48 | 52–56 | Moon
— | 57–60 | Puzzle
49–56 | 61–64 | Rogue
